<L>__{exterior freeman's slave pen later}
<A>__{the slaves are in various states of undress, men and women alike. they clean themselves, scrubbing with soap and water. women wash their hair. men shave, skin is oiled. freeman walks among them, inspecting them as they primp themselves.}
<L>__{interior freeman's slave pen later}
<A>__{the slaves are given new clothes by cape. the men are given hat, coat, shirt, pants and shoes. the women frocks of calico and handkerchiefs to bind about their heads.}
